show.description: In the glittering world of the Rathods, billionaire heiress Avantika lives undercover as house staff, hiding her power from husband Sheel. When scheming Rutuja plots a hostile takeover, Avantika must reveal her true identity to reclaim her empire—and exact revenge in a high-stakes battle of queens.
